data.description: Stop making your landlord rich in 2024 and purchase to create wealth! Realtor's MLS shows there has not been a 1bedrm available since 2022! So don't let this opportunity pass you by! This one bedroom, 1.5 bath, townhome will be ready for new owners very shortly! The Glen Oaks Townhome community offers a north Dallas address, in the  prestigious Lake Highlands corridor! Minutes from I635, Tom Thumb and shopping at Royal Lane and Skillman!  Heading towards Walnut Hill, you will find, Lake Highlands Freshman Center, High School, Recreation Center, Towne Center, fitness, shopping and eating galore! DART routes are also available in this area! Owner is packing and pics will be taken this week!
